      "textAlign": "left",
      "letterSpacing": 0.4
    },
    {
      "id": "el-122",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16,
      "y": 1228,
      "content": "When Ramp onboarded 40,000 new cards in Q3, their legacy fraud scoring could not keep pace with novel attack vectors targeting corporate spend management.",
      "fontSize": 13.5,
